{"tid":2095118,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中國用DNA加強社會監控","createTime":"2020-07-05T08:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:10:16.000Z","uid":343610,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ad39f6d4c913894e89ebce69af4e57b5ec9f0a24","tid":2095118,"uid":343610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"雖然篇新聞已經係上年十二月，但真係想提提大家明日新疆，今日香港。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nresearch 完睇到佢對新疆同西藏都係咁，可以預計到香港人嘅下場。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，新疆圖木舒克市<span style=\"color: red;\">當局採集了當地數百名維吾爾人的血液樣本，並據此建立基因資料庫，分析基因型與個人外觀特徵和家族血統的相對關係，以產出相應的人臉圖像。</span><br />\n<br />\n儘管相關技術在中國仍處於早期發展階段，所產出人臉圖像的品質僅能用於縮小「肉搜」範圍和排除特徵不合的犯嫌，專家憂心，當局的真正意圖是打造有效工具，以強化對維吾爾族的歧視性政策。<br />\n<br />\n專家認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">當局未來甚至可將根據基因資料庫建立的人臉圖像輸入遍布新疆的人臉辨識和大規模監控系統，以加強偵測異議份子和罪犯，提升社會控制強度。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以縮窄搜尋範圍 增加效率</span><br />\n<br />\n根據報道，部分相關研究在中國公安部營運的實驗室進行，且至少有兩名和公安部合作的中國科學家曾接受歐洲聲譽良好的研究機構資助，國際性科學期刊也曾在未檢視基因樣本來源的情況下刊登他們的研究。<br />\n<br />\n儘管這些中國科學家聲稱，他們的研究方法符合國際學術規範，包括採集生物樣本需事先取得被取樣者同意，新疆地區居民其實沒有選擇。一些逃離當地的維吾爾人指控，當局強迫居民接受健康檢查並藉機採集他們的生物樣本。<br />\n<br />\n而就算沒有維吾爾族的「貢獻」，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國也擁有全世界規模最大的基因資料庫。綜合當地媒體報道，至今年7月，中國已握有超過8000萬筆基因檔案。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kSCcYy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kSCcYy.png&h=0ae7b64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2512442/【新疆人權法】紐約時報：借助西方技術%20新疆用DNA繪製人臉加強社會監控\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2512442%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9A%E5%80%9F%E5%8A%A9%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%2520%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%94%A8DNA%E7%B9%AA%E8%A3%BD%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=e2cdddc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2512442/【新疆人權法】紐約時報：借助西方技術%20新疆用DNA繪製人臉加強社會監控</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">諗起幾日前嘅新聞，警方向十名涉違反《港區國安法》被捕者檢取DNA樣本</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535697-20200703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535697-20200703.htm&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=d72706c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535697-20200703.htm&h=65478762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535697-20200703.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cdaccfffaf7d2b06f5e70ffd2844738a911c97d4","tid":2095118,"uid":343610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人唔知佢拎DNA做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家關注下71反國安法嘅被捕人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc36f8b77ec8689162998790b460ac513327b83","tid":2095118,"uid":51066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6356260503241e2d90096b27c0743a125dbfe8d","tid":2095118,"uid":343610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc36f8b77ec8689162998790b460ac513327b83","tid":2095118,"uid":51066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"遲吓香港人就會好似猶太人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm